# Project Structure

```text
ATM-Verification-Framework
│
├── src/
│   └── atm_fsm.v                 # RTL Design
│
├── sim/
│   ├── atm_server.py            # Python simulation engine
│   └── run_native.py
│
├── tests/
│   ├── test_atm_server.py
│   ├── test_edge_cases.py
│   ├── test_randomized.py
│   ├── test_coverage.py
│   └── test_transition_coverage.py
│
├── scripts/
│   ├── generate_coverage.py
│   ├── generate_dashboard.py
│   └── clean.py
│
├── reports/
│   ├── dashboard.html
│   ├── dashboard.png
│   ├── fsm.png
│   ├── waveform.png
│   ├── coverage.txt
│   └── summary.json
│
├── run_demo.py
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

---

# Technology Stack

| Category | Tools |
|----------|--------|
| RTL Design | Verilog |
| Simulation | Icarus Verilog |
| Waveform Analysis | GTKWave |
| Verification | Python, unittest |
| Reporting | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| Coverage | Custom State & Transition Coverage Engine |

---

# Getting Started

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<username>/ATM-Verification-Framework.git
cd ATM-Verification-Framework
```

---

## Install Requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
sudo apt install iverilog gtkwave
```

---

# Run Complete Verification Flow

```bash
python run_demo.py
```

This command automatically:

- Runs all unit tests
- Executes randomized scenarios
- Generates coverage reports
- Builds the verification dashboard

---

# Run Individual Components

### Unit Tests

```bash
python -m unittest discover tests -v
```

### Coverage Report

```bash
python -m scripts.generate_coverage
```

### Single Simulation

```bash
python -m sim.run_native
```

### Dashboard Generation

```bash
python -m scripts.generate_dashboard
```

